<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>The Triple-i Initiative 2026 will air on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20260409T1600" target="_blank" rel="noopener">April 9 at 9:00 a.m. PT / 12:00 p.m. ET</a>, organizer <a title="Companies > Evil Empire [24 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/evil-empire">Evil Empire</a> announced. You will be able to watch it on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@iii_initiative" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a> and <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/iii_initiative" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitch</a>. <span id="more-1034602"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature over 45 minutes of “back-to-back announcements with zero fluff,” including eight world premieres, gameplay reveals, and release dates. Confirmed publishers include <a title="Companies > Devolver Digital [441 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/devolver-digital">Devolver Digital</a>, <a title="Companies > Klei [28 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/klei">Klei</a>, <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:r3nrysx4ddakwnpunxr3c5iu/post/3mhdxrbdosx2i" target="_blank">sunset visitor</a>, and <a title="Companies > tinyBuild [161 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/tinybuild">tinyBuild</a>. Confirmed games include <em><a title="Games > Alkahest [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/alkahest">Alkahest</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Castlevania: Belmont's Curse [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/castlevania-belmonts-curse">Castlevania: Belmont’s Curse</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Dead as Disco [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dead-as-disco">Dead as Disco</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Risk of Rain 2 [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/risk-of-rain-2">Risk of Rain 2</a></em>, and <em><a title="Games > Windrose [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/windrose">Windrose</a></em>. A post-show with deep dives on some of the featured titles from the showcase will follow.</p><p>Watch a teaser trailer below.</p><h2><span>Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="The Triple-i Initiative showcase returns on April 9th!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3AsSAM2EWKw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
